Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.61,0:00:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾出本山
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.79,0:00:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日复一日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.94,0:00:24.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羊肠小路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.55,0:00:39.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安达之原
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.61,0:00:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}节选自谣曲:『黑塚』舞者表演的为日本传统舞台艺术『能』

Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.59,0:04:44.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九郎少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.87,0:04:47.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些人 不是镰仓的兵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.32,0:04:56.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 不过想杀源义经的并非只有您哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.56,0:05:00.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知还有多少人想要取您的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.50,0:05:02.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.88,0:05:07.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,源氏从平家手中夺取天下之后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.59,0:05:09.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最为危险的就是我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.08,0:05:14.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弁庆 你若取下我的人头
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.28,0:05:17.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少还能保住性命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.47,0:05:18.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九郎少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.63,0:05:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我辈已经活得够久 战得够多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.42,0:05:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 到此结束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.24,0:05:29.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您怎能这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.36,0:05:34.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 弁庆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:38.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九郎少爷 那里有火光
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.45,0:05:40.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火光？ 是追兵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.21,0:05:43.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那火光没有移动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.42,0:05:46.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应是人家的灯光吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.94,0:05:49.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道还有人住在这深山里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.42,0:05:54.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除我们之外还有其他远离俗世之人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.63,0:05:59.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天色已晚 水也不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.49,0:06:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若是人家 就去借宿一晚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.82,0:06:05.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 以防万一
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:09.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九郎之名暂由我弁庆代为使用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.35,0:06:43.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.67,0:06:47.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.35,0:06:52.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问有人在家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.57,0:06:56.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.77,0:07:14.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有何贵干
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.76,0:07:24.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:31.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我是自纪州熊野而来 周游各国的僧侣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.60,0:07:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名为九郎坊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:35.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路经此山时
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.67,0:07:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,适逢天色已晚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:44.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,土间或屋檐都行 能否让我们在此借宿一晚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:44.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}土间：日本以前民居中露出泥地的房间 一般为进屋后脱鞋的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.51,0:07:51.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决不会给您添麻…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.41,0:07:52.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您的随同…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:01.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.48,0:08:09.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好高的烧 不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.35,0:08:13.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.08,0:08:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位是你的弟子？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:18.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:27.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但您的身上有难以掩饰的高贵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.17,0:08:30.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仿佛那位僧侣才是您的弟子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.97,0:08:41.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:44.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以让你们住下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.64,0:08:47.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但有一个要求
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.33,0:08:51.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这屋子最里面有个房间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.94,0:08:54.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我的闺房
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.86,0:08:57.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面久未整理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.58,0:09:02.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何请不要往里看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.12,0:09:05.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了 小事一桩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.75,0:09:09.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能答应这个要求
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.09,0:09:11.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管多久
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.28,0:09:15.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都可以住在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.50,0:09:19.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.74,0:09:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫黑蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.21,0:09:37.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他好一点了么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.22,0:09:40.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像还没有太大起色
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.98,0:09:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打算下山买些药
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:46.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这期间 那位大人就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.61,0:09:48.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.43,0:10:40.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烧已经退了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.43,0:10:42.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.89,0:10:44.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是您在照顾我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.06,0:10:45.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:02.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说好借宿一晚的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.34,0:11:05.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等同伴回来我们马上就走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.90,0:11:07.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.47,0:11:12.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要您愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.20,0:11:16.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论多久都可以住在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.81,0:11:23.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论多久
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.21,0:11:56.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.50,0:12:10.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里和我至今所在的世界完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.52,0:12:14.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它存在于时间和空间之外
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.23,0:12:17.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 就是这些树木
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.84,0:12:19.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经活了上千年了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 黑蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.12,0:12:35.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天您会离开这儿的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.47,0:13:08.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我大概是疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.34,0:13:18.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.93,0:13:21.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论我们再怎么彼此相爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.55,0:13:24.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命运决定了我和您
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.52,0:13:29.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不能在一起生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.68,0:14:20.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.51,0:14:22.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弁庆回来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.94,0:14:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.77,0:14:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是弁庆的话应该会先来这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.22,0:14:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追兵？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.87,0:14:36.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有动静
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:50.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是里间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.01,0:15:50.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何请不要往里看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.55,0:16:25.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.39,0:16:35.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您觉得我很肮脏是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.02,0:16:40.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 这样也好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.46,0:16:44.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道总会有这样一天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.32,0:16:56.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我心中一直无意识地 盼望着您能看到这样的我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.90,0:17:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.47,0:17:04.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天看到的一切我不会告诉别人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.47,0:17:17.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑蜜！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.77,0:18:21.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畜生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.21,0:19:02.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我赢了 义经
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.20,0:19:24.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不死？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.30,0:19:28.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说那个女人不会死？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.61,0:19:30.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.64,0:19:38.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其女命逾百年而不老 乃不死之身
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.59,0:19:45.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾族从平安京时代起就一直追杀着她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.86,0:19:46.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老丈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.96,0:19:50.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你准备抓她来如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.15,0:19:56.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解开……
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.97,0:19:59.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不死的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.81,0:20:08.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.33,0:20:13.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.87,0:20:14.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,右臂…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.71,0:20:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.47,0:20:25.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身体不同常人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.43,0:20:32.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本不想让您知道这肮脏之躯的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.02,0:20:36.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.30,0:20:41.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经活不长了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.02,0:20:46.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就会死在这荒山里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.06,0:20:53.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我留下 自己逃跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.08,0:21:09.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.00,0:21:13.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您愿与我同行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.24,0:21:18.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.88,0:21:26.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间的尽头
